modName: Simple ENB FXaa SMaa SweetFX Batch Uninstaller
summary: Easily remove files from ENB, FXaa, SMaa, and SweetFX configs
descriptionHtml:
[b][u][size=5]Description[/size][/u][/b]
This is a small, easy to edit, batch file that removes files from [b]ENB, FXaa, SMaa, SweetFX,[/b] and a couple of logs that are not needed.

Some files/folders not being removed? Comment or message me on [url=http://steamcommunity.com/id/thejman494]Steam[/url] and I will add it to the list, I will give credit where credit is due.


[img]http://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/49027-1-1387597786.gif[/img]

     [b][u][size=5]Instructions[/size][/u][/b]
Simply download and put in your Skyrim root folder and run it. (Where TESV.exe is)


Here's a list of files and folders that are currently in the list in alphabetical order,
For those who want to check before downloading
